{\pard{\tx432 \qj\li0\fi0\ri0\sb0\sl0\sa0 \plain\f2\fs28\cf0\b Sentencia C-279/13\par
\qj\li0\fi0\ri0\sb0\sl0\sa0 \plain\f2\fs28\cf0\b \par
